The '''Mark V-rated torpedo''' was a type of [[Proton torpedo/Legends|proton torpedo]].<ref name="BG">{{JournalCite|5|A Buyer's Guide to Alternative Starships}}</ref>

Standard models of the [[Arakyd Industries/Legends|Arakyd Industries]] [[Helix-class light interceptor]] were designed to carry five of them.<ref name="BG" />

